actionAppleScript.inline: if application "Mattermost" is running then  tell application "System Events"  if visible of process "Mattermost" then  tell application "Finder" to set visible of process "Mattermost" to false  else  tell application "Finder" to set visible of process "Mattermost" to true  activate application "Mattermost"  end if  end tell  else  tell application "Mattermost" to activate  end if

if application "Telegram" is running then  tell application "System Events"  if visible of process "Telegram" then  tell application "Finder" to set visible of process "Telegram" to false  else  tell application "Finder" to set visible of process "Telegram" to true  activate application "Telegram"  end if  end tell  else  tell application "Telegram" to activate  end if

source.inline: title=$(exec /opt/homebrew/bin/nowplaying-cli get title); artist=$(exec /opt/homebrew/bin/nowplaying-cli get artist); if [[ $title != "null" && $artist != "null" ]]; then echo "$title" - "$artist"; else echo "Nothing is playing right now"; fi

actionAppleScript.inline: trytell application "System Events"set visible of process "Yandex Music" to not visible of process "Yandex Music"if visible of process "Yandex Music" thentell application "Яндекс Музыка" to activateend ifend tellon errortell application "Яндекс Музыка" to activateend try

activate application "Activity Monitor"tell application "System Events"	tell process "Activity Monitor"		tell radio button "CPU" of radio group 1 of group 2 of toolbar 1 of window 1 to perform action "AXPress"	end tellend tell
